      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is a bit dicey; winio returns an internal pipe type which embeds an internal file type, which exposes a public Fd() method. os.NewFile creates a wrapper (not a duplicate) around the os-specific file descriptor type (in this case, a windows HANDLE).\n\nClosing this `NewFile` will close the underlying pipe (since the File in this case is just a thin wrapper).",
